Kim-ku3: Lin2 tioh8 soe2 lai5 ka-ki7 chheng-khi3; tui3 Goa2 e5 bak8-chiu cheng5 tu5-khi3 lin2 sou2 kiann5 e5 phainn2. (I2-sai3-a 1:16)
I2-cheng5 u7 chit8 e5 thoan5-to7 e5 lang5, si3-koe3 chhut-khi3 thoan5 hok-im kio3 lang5 hoan2-hoe2 sin3 Ia5-sou. I sou2 toa3 e5 mih8-kiann7 chin kan2-tan, chi2-u7 chit8-pun2 Seng3-keng, cha2-am3 thang thak8, chit8-ki teng-hoe2 thang ti7 am3-si5 thak8 Seng3-keng, chit8-chiah ke-kak, cha2-khi2 si5 thang kio3 i khi2-lai5 thak8 Seng3-keng, chit8-chiah be2 thang khia5 khi3 si3-koe3 thoan5-to7, an2-ni na7-tiann7.
U7 chit8-pai2 kau3 ti7 chit8 e5 soann-kan e5 sio2 hiunn-sia7. I chiu7 jip8-khi3 ti7 hia kio3 lang5 tioh8 hoan2-hoe2, tu5-khi3 tak8-hang7 e5 phainn2, tui3 Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih lai5 soe2 sim-lai7 hou7 chheng-khi3. Chong2-si7 chit-chng e5 lang5 tak8-e5 chin phainn2, chin hiong-ok, m7-na7 m7 hoe2-kai2 lai5 sin3 Ia5-sou, hoan2-tng2 koann2 chit e5 thoan5-to7 e5 lang5 chhut in e5 hiunn-sia7, chit e5 lang5 kou-put-chiong chhut chit e5 chng-goa7, in-ui7 i2-keng am3, chiu7 ti7 hu7-kin7 e5 chhiu7-kha hioh mi5. I kam2-kak chin kan-khou2; chiah-nih koann5 ia7 bo5 chhu3-teng2 jia hou7, ia7 bo5 piah thang jia hong, m7-ku2 i e5 sim ia7-si7 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, siunn7 kong2 Siong7-te3 sou2 choe3 e5 long2 si7 tioh8, chiu7 tiam2 teng-hoe2 thak8 Seng3-keng, chong2-si7 bo5 joa7-ku2 chit8-chun7 hong lai5, chiong teng-hoe2 thau3-hoa. I siunn7 kong2, tann si7 chainn2-iunn7, lian7 beh thak8 Seng3-keng iah8 bo5 hoe2?
Chong2-si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 choe3 e5 long2 si7 tioh8, chiu7 siunn7 beh khun3, hit si5 chit8-chiah chhai5-long5 lai5, tui3 hit chiah ke-kak ka7 teh chau2. I chiah thou2-khui3 kong2, goa2 chainn2-iunn7 chiah put-heng7, lian5 cha2-khi2-si5 thang kio3 goa2 khi2--lai5 thak8 Seng3-keng e5 ke-a2 iah8 bo5 khi3, chong2-si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 cho3 e5 bo5 m7-tioh8. Tu2 teh kong2 e5 si5 chit8-chiah sai chhut-lai5, i kiann kau3 phih8-phih8-chhoah, hit-chiah sai khoann3-tioh8 be2 chiu7 ka7 ka7-khi3 chiah8. Sou2-i2 i chin siong-pi. Ah! Goa2 sou2 u7 e5 tang5-phoann7 long2 bo5 khi3 lah, tann beh chainn2-iunn7, chong2-si7 koh siunn7 Siong7-te3 sou2 cho3 e5 long2 si7 ho2 e5, hit-am3 in-ui7 chin sian7 chiu7 khun3-khi3, chit8-chhinn2 kau3 thinn-kng, keh cha2-khi2 i jip8-khi3 chng-lai7 chiah tioh8 toa7-kiann. In-ui7 cha-am3 chit8-tin7 kiong5-to7 lai5 chhiunn2-kiap, sou2 u7 e5 lang5 long2 thai5-si2, sou2-u7 e5 mih8-kiann7 long2 chhiunn2 liau2-liau2.
I chiah siunn7 tioh8 Siong7-te3 tui3 i e5 thiann3, cha-am3 teng-hoe2 na7 bo5 hou7 hong thau3-hoa, kiong5-to7 tek-khak oe7 khoann3-tioh8 kng lai5 hai7 i, ke kap be2 na7 bo5 hou7 ia2-siu3 ka7-khi3, tek-khak thiann-tioh8 chhat8-be2 e5 siann oe7 tioh8 kiann chhut-siann, kiong5-to7 ia7 oe7 hoat-kak i ti7 hia, sou2-i2 i chiu7 ti7-hia kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 tui3 i hiah-nih8 toa7 e5 thiann3.
Sio2 peng5-iu2, Siong7-te3 u7 thiann3 hit e5 sim chheng-khi3 e5 thoan5-to7 e5 lang5, chong2-si7 hiah e5 chng-nih8 e5 lang5, m7 hoan2-hoe2 tu5-khi3 in sou2 kiann5 e5 phainn2. Sou2-i2 Siong7-te3 hou7 in tu2-tioh8 hit-khoan2 e5 chai-e7, lan2 tioh8 chhin-chhiunn7 chit e5 thoan5-to7 e5 lang5 sim chheng-khi3. (Liam7 kim-ku3) (T. T. T.)
