Kim-ku3: Ia5-ho5-hoa ah, kiu5 Li2 chiong Li2 e5 to7-lou7 chi2-si7 goa2; goa2 beh chiau3 Li2 e5 chin-li2 lai5 kiann5. (Si-phian 86:11)
Hak8-seng, goa2 lai5 mng7 kui2-ku3, khoann3 lin2 u7 ho2 ki3-ti5 a2-bo2? Goa2 bat kong2 chit8 e5 ong5 chin gau5, u7 khi2 Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 seng3-tian7, koh ia7 u7 sia2 Seng3-keng tiong e5 kui2-na7-pun2, hit e5 ong5 kio3 choe3 sim2-mih8 mia5?...... Hit e5 ong5 kau3 ni5-lau7, i e5 phin2-heng7 soa3 pinn3 chainn2-iunn7?...... Ui7-tioh8 an2-ni i u7 chhut chit8 e5 put-siau3 e5 kiann2, bo5 chhin-chhiunn7 i hiah gau5, koh m7-thiann lau7-lang5 e5 khou2-khng3, hit e5 kiann2 kio3-choe3 sim2-mih8 mia5?...... Kau3 hit si5 I2-sek-liat8-kok chiu7 pinn3-choe3 chainn2-iunn7?......
An2-ni tioh8, tann tui3 kok-ka hun-lih8 liau2-au7 Lam5-tiau5 te7-it tai7 e5 ong5 kio3 choe3 Lo5-pho-am3, chiu7-si7 lin2 tu2-a2 sou2 kong2 hit e5. Te7 2 tai7 kio3 choe3 A-pi2-iang2, te7 3 tai7 A-sat. Tann lan2 cha2-khi2 beh sann-kap lai5 hak8-sip8 te7 4 tai7, chiu7-si7 A-sat e5 kiann2 Iok-sa-hoat ong5 e5 su7. Chit e5 u7 chin thang kho2-chhu2 e5 sou2-chai7.
Tng i che7-ui7 e5 si5, i jiat8-sim keng3-pai3 Siong7-te3. Chhe lang5 kau3 tak8 e5 soann-thau5, chiong in chou2 Sou2-lo5-bun5 ui7-tioh8 hiah e5 phian-hui sou2 khi2 e5 put8-toann5 long2 ka7 in hui2-hoai7, koh si3-ke3 thoan5 Siong7-te3 e5 ka3-si7 kio3 peh-sinn3 lai5 siu2. Tui3 an2-ni i e5 kok chiu7 toa7 heng.
Na7-si7 u7 chit8-jit8 hut-jian5 u7 tui3-tek8 sann-kok lian5-beng5 beh lai5 kong-kek Iu5-tai7 kok. (Lam5-tiau5 hit si5 kio3-choe3 Iu5-tai7, Pak-tiau5 kio3-choe3 I2-sek-liat8.) Chiu7-si7 Mou5-ap, A-bun5, Bi2-ou-ni5 e5 lian5-hap8-kun, long2 bo5 choh-siann, hut-jian5 bo5 phah-sng3, khi2 tai7-kun lai5 phah Iu5-tai7. Iok-sa-hoat ong5 chit8-si5 toa7-kiann, in-ui7 long2 bo5 pi7-pan7. Koh si7 3 kok e5 lian5-hap8-kun, peng-be2 chian3-khi3 chian3-chhia beng2-chiong3 chin-che7. Se3-bin7 chin-toa7, hoa7-hoa7-hau2 tit8-tit8 lai5, siu2 pian-kai3 e5 peng chau2-lai5 po3, kong2 tek8-kun i2-keng lai5 kau3 Un2-ki-ti2 chiu7-si7 Iu5-tai7 e5 kok-keng2, tann ong5 li2 tioh8 kin2 siat-hoat. Ong5 chit8 si5 siunn7 bo5 pou7, beh thoan5-leng7 cheng3 peng-be2 ma7 be7 hu3, tann beh an2-choann2.
Hit si5 ong5 siunn7 kau3 chin bo5 pou7, the3 bo5 lou7. I chi2-u7 kui7-loh8 ng3 Ia5-ho5-hoa au5-kio3, koh thoan5-leng7 hou7 thong kok beng7-leng7 cheng3 peh-sinn3 tioh8 kim3-chiah8. Koh kio3 tak8-siann5 e5 peh-sinn3 tioh8 kio3 tai7-piau2 kau3 Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 tian7 sann-kap ki5-to2 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5. Li2 khoann3 che si7 ho5-teng2 e5 chhim-sin3. Tui3-tek8 kau3, te7-it e5 ho7-leng7 m7 si7 tiau3-chip8 kun-peng, be2-tui7 chian3-chhia. I sou2 hoat e5 te7-it beng7-leng7 si7 kio3 lang5 kim3-chiah8, tiau3 tai7-piau2 kau3 seng3-tian7 ki5-to2. I pun2-sin ia7 kim3-chiah8 kui7 ti7 Seng3-tian7, ti7 Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 bin7-cheng5 lai5 ki5-to2.
Keh-jit8 ong5 chiu7 tiau3-chip8 peh-sinn3 ti7 The5-ko-a e5 khong3-ia2, tui3 peh-sinn3 soan-gian5 kong2, ¡§Peh-sinn3 ah, tioh8 thiann goa2, lin2 tioh8 sin3 Ia5-ho5-hoa lin2 e5 Siong7-te3, chiu7 beh khia7-chai7; sin3 I e5 sian-ti chiu7 beh heng-thong.¡¨
Kong2-soah chiu7 siat-lip8 chhiunn3-koa-tui7, hou7 in chheng7 seng3 koh sui2 e5 sann kiann5 ti7 kun-tui7 e5 thau5-cheng5 o-lo2 Ia5-ho5-hoa, chhiunn3 kong2, ¡§Tioh8 kam2-sia7 Ia5-ho5-hoa; in-ui7 I e5 chu5-ai3 eng2-oan2 ti7-teh.¡¨ Lin2 thiann liau2 kam2-kak chainn2-iunn7? Na2 u7 hiah sim-sek, a2-si7 hiah gong7 e5 kau-chian3 hoat. M7 tioh8 kio3 be2-peng, a2-si7 chian3-chhia choe3 thau5-cheng5. Sim2-mih8 kio3 seng3-koa-tui7 chheng7 sui2-sann, gim5-si kiann5 choe3 thau5-cheng5. To m7-si7 beh iu5-heng5 ngia5 lau7-jiat8, kiann5 ke-lou7--e5, tui3-tek8 khoann3-tioh8 ma7 ai3-chhio3. Na7-si7 Iok-sa-hoat ong5 i chai, kau-chian3 tek-seng3 m7 si7 chai7-ti7 i kap i e5 kun-peng, si7 chai7-ti7 Ia5-ho5-hoa.
Tann an2-choann2, Seng3-keng e5 lek8-su2 sia2 kong2, ¡§In tu2-a2 chhiunn3-koa o-lo2 e5 si5, Ia5-ho5-hoa chiu7 phai3 bai5-hok8 e5 thinn-peng kong-kek hiah e5 lai5 kong-kek Iu5-tai7 e5 A-bun5, Mou5-ap kap Se-jinn2-soann e5 lang5; in chiu7 siu7 phah.¡¨ (II Lek8-tai7 20: 22) Siong7-te3 hou7 in 3 kok e5 peng ka-ti7 khi2-lai5 loan7, ka-ti7 sio-thai5, ka-ti7 thai5-si2 liau2-liau2.
Tui3 an2-ni Iu5-tai7 e5 peng long2 m7-bian2 tang7-khi2 chhiunn-to, ia7 bo5 sit-loh8 chit8 e5, chiu7 tit-tioh8 choan5-seng3. Ong5 chhoa7 kun-peng lai5 tit-tioh8 chian3-li7-phin2. Peh-sinn3 long2 chhut-lai5 chhiunn2 chian3-li7-phin2 tit-tioh8 chai5-but8, i-hok8, po2-poe3, che7 kau3 theh8 be7 kiann5. An2-ni lian5-lian5 chhiunn2-mih8 3 jit8 ku2. Toa7 tek-seng3 khai2-soan5. Te7 4 jit8 cheng3 peh-sinn3 kap Iok-sa-hoat ong5 long2 chu7-chip8 ti7 Pi2-lah8-ka e5 soann-kok ti7 hia lai5 o-lo2 Siong7-te3. Tui3 an2-ni tui3-tek8 long2 m7-kann2 koh lai5, koh toa7 thai3-peng5, in-ui7 Siong7-te3 siunn2-su3 in peng5-an. Hak8-seng, li2 thiann liau2 u7 chhu3-bi7, u7 kam2-kek a2-bo5? Chhin-chhiunn7 an2-ni, lan2 ia7 tioh8 si5-si5 than3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 lai5 kiann5. (Sann-kap lai5 liam7 kim-ku3) (L. J. S. sia2)
