Kim-ku3: Sou2-i2 goan2 ia7 beh hok8-sai7 Ia5-ho5-hoa, in-ui7 I si7 goan2 e5 Siong7-te3. (Iok-su-a 24: 18)
Chit e5 kou3-su7 chiu7-si7 Jit8-pun2 teh koan2 Tai5-oan5 e5 si5-chun7 e5 tai7-chi3. Ti7 chit8 e5 sou2-chai7 e5 kau3-hoe7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 hak8-seng si7 12 hoe3 e5 sio2 peng5-iu2. I e5 pa-pa si7 in e5 kau3-hoe7 e5 tiunn2-lo2 choan5 ka-chok8 chin-chiann3 jiat8-sim pai3 Siong7-te3, cha2, am3, siong5-siong5 choe3 ka-teng5 le2-pai3, chong2-si7 Jit8-pun2 cheng3-hu2 chin bo5 hoann-hi2 Tai5-oan5 lang5 pai3 Siong7-te3, in-ui7 in ai3 lan2 hok8-sai7 in e5 kok-sin5 kio3-choe3 ¡§A-ma-the-la-su3¡¨ e5 sin5, ia7 ai3 lan2 kui7-pai3 in e5 hong5-te3 kio3-choe3 ¡§Thian-no2-he2-kha3¡¨ sou2-i2 khoann3 lan2 Ki-tok-tou5 jiat8-sim pai3 Siong7-te3 in chiu7 chin chu3-i3 ai3 chhe7 ki-hoe7 lai5 chou2-tong3.
